<span class="margnote"><span id="an_000">job 14:0</span></span>

Overview

[Job 14:1](../../../bib/kjv/job014.htm#001.md), Job entreats God for
favour, by the shortness of life, and certainty of death; [Job
14:7](../../../bib/kjv/job014.htm#007.md), He waits for his change; [Job
14:16](../../../bib/kjv/job014.htm#016.md), By sin the creature is subject
to corruption.

